* Firebase (Database)
- https://console.firebase.google.com/u/0/project/netflix-clone-97f22/overview

* Create React Project
- netflix-clone
	* Install firebase (Get this code in firebase) 
	- npm install -g firebase-tools
	* For API functions
	- npm i axios
	* trailer pop-ups
	- npm i react-youtube
	- npm i movie-trailer
	
* Deployment
- npm run build
- firebase login
- firebase init
- Are you ready to proceed? Yes
- Hosting
- existing project 
- What do you want to use as your public directory? build
- Configure as a single-page app (rewrite all urls to /index.html)? Yes
- npm run build
- firebase deploy

Project Console: https://console.firebase.google.com/project/netflix-clone-97f22/overview
Hosting URL: https://netflix-clone-97f22.web.app